      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/main/java/org/onap/vid/controller/MsoConfig.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 58,
      "message": "For unirestObjectMapper to handle Kotlin, I think we can set this in WebConfig (adding the `registerModule(new KotlinModule()`):\n\n```\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.module.kotlin.KotlinModule;\n\n\n    @Bean\n    public com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper getObjectMapper() {\n        return new com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper().registerModule(new KotlinModule());\n    }\n\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4379,
        "name": "Ittay Stern",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "ittay.stern@att.com",
        "username": "ittays"
